The '''yellow-bellied longbill''' or '''green-crowned longbill''' ('''''Toxorhamphus novaeguineae''''') is a species of [[bird]] in the family [[Melanocharitidae]]. It is found in [[New Guinea]]. Its natural [[habitat]]s are [[subtropical or tropical moist lowland forest]] and subtropical or tropical moist [[montane forest]].

